1. Introduction
At ReByte, we believe in a simple principle: your data is yours.
We built this platform with your privacy in mind ‚Äî no surveillance, no hidden trackers, and no selling of your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and what control you have over it.

2. Information We Collect
We only collect minimal and necessary information to provide the core functionality of the app. Here's what we collect:

a. Account Information
When you sign up: we collect your username, email (optional), and contact preferences (e.g., phone, Viber, WhatsApp, or Facebook link).

b. Listing Data
If you post a listing: we store the information you provide (title, description, price, location, category, images, etc.).

c. Device Information
We may collect non-identifiable device data (OS version, app version) to improve performance and debug issues. This data is not linked to your identity.

d. Optional Preferences
Settings you choose (e.g., grid vs. list view, saved listings) are stored locally or securely tied to your account.

3. What We Do Not Do
‚ùå We do not track your browsing behavior outside the app

‚ùå We do not use third-party analytics that profile or fingerprint you

‚ùå We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data to advertisers or marketers

‚ùå We do not collect unnecessary background data

4. How We Use Your Information
We use your data only to operate and improve the app, including:

Displaying and managing your listings

Enabling contact between buyers and sellers

Saving your preferences for a smoother experience

Improving app performance and reliability

5. Data Sharing
We do not share your data with any third-party advertisers or data brokers.

We may share data only in the following cases:

With your consent (e.g., when you publicly post a listing)

For legal reasons, if required to comply with law enforcement or legal obligations

With service providers directly involved in operating the platform (e.g., secure cloud storage), under strict confidentiality

6. Data Retention
Account and listing data is retained while your account is active.

You can request deletion of your account and all related data at any time via [support email or in-app option].

7. Your Rights and Controls
You have full control over your data:

‚úÖ View or edit your profile

‚úÖ Delete your listings or account

‚úÖ Control which contact options are visible

‚úÖ Request data export or deletion by contacting us

We respond to all privacy requests within a reasonable timeframe.

8. Children's Privacy
ReByte is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.

9. Security
We use industry-standard encryption and access controls to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

10. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy from time to time. If we make material changes, we‚Äôll notify you in-app or via email. Your continued use of ReByte means you agree to the updated policy.

